<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@finsweet/attributes-richtext@1/richtext.js"></script></head><body><div data-animation="default" class="c-header w-nav" data-easing2="ease" data-easing="ease" data-collapse="small" role="banner" data-no-scroll="1" data-duration="400" data-doc-height="1"><div class="c-header_container w-container"><a href="/" class="c-header_logocontainer w-nav-brand"><img src="/assets/img/66cd04e4e07d61b2beb0424b_productivity-nexus_logo.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Productivity Nexus"/></a><nav role="navigation" class="c-header_menu w-nav-menu"><a href="https://form.nutt.ai/consulting" target="_blank" class="c-header_link w-nav-link">1:1 Consulting</a><a href="/" class="c-header_link subscribe w-nav-link">Subscribe</a></nav><div class="c-header_hamburger w-nav-button"><div class="w-icon-nav-menu"></div></div></div></div><h1>3 AI Productivity Hacks That&#x27;ll Save You an Eternity</h1><div class="g-container w-richtext"><p><em>Here are three AI-adjacent productivity hacks I&#x27;m loving and sure you will, too:</em></p><h3>1. Don&#x27;t type. Speak!</h3><p>Speaking is 4x faster than typing.</p><ul role="list"><li><a target="_blank" href="https://ref.wisprflow.ai/william-nutt">Wispr</a> transcribes and polishes my spoken word across apps—desktop and mobile.</li><li>With <a target="_blank" href="https://voicenotes.com/?via=william-nutt">Voicenotes</a>, I can ramble endlessly about any idea, then it&#x27;ll tidy and format it for any need.</li></ul><h3>2. Save prompts as snippets.</h3><ul role="list"><li>I use <a target="_blank" href="https://www.raycast.com/">Raycast</a> to make my reused prompts available in a few taps of the keyboard. They&#x27;re configured with variables for the inputs that change.</li><li><a target="_blank" href="https://blaze.today/?ref=UFY5Y82L">Text Blaze</a> is an interesting new browser extension that serves the same function.</li></ul><h3>3. Chat with multiple bots.</h3><p>No AI chatbot is best for every prompt. If you want the most useful output, prompting multiple chatbots is a must.</p><ul role="list"><li>Tools like <a target="_blank" href="https://chathub.gg/">ChatHub</a> and <a target="_blank" href="https://magai.co/?via=william-nutt">Magai</a> make it easy.</li></ul><p>‍</p><p><em>Susbscribe to </em><a href=""><em>Productivity Nexus</em></a><em> for more empmowering insights around AI, automation and systemization.</em></p></div><script src="/assets/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js" type="text/javascript" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="/assets/js/webflow.schunk.js" type="text/javascript" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="/assets/js/webflow.alt.js" type="text/javascript" crossorigin="anonymous"></script></body></html>